### Hadith 4:586

*Narrated Anas bin Malik:*

When the mountain of Uhud came in the sight of Allah's Apostle he said.
"This is a mountain that loves us and is loved by us. O Allah! Abraham
made Mecca a sanctuary, and I make (the area) in between these two
mountains (of Medina) a sanctuary."

